									<a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/a44be2e7-fa44-4c6b-9bd8-f545b161c450/public_url" target="_blank" class="font-bold">AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner</a>
									<p class="italic text-gray-500 text-sm text-end">2025</p>
